headline.main: MUNICIPAL.; THE ALDERMEN. The Aldermen met last evening, President BARKER in the Chair. A communication was received from the appointing Isaac Bell, Jr., and W. S. Duke a Committee to confer with a similar one from the Alderman on the subject of the new prison in the rear of Essex Market.
